    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rods or slips of wood designed for personal reading, used for following words on a page; may be highly decorative and of a type used in the Early Christian and Medieval periods.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
